Title: Ideal Spares main burner
Description: An Ideal replacement main burner for selected Ideal boilers. The burner produces heat in a combustible heating appliance. In natural gas appliances gas is transferred to a gas valve and into the burner for ignition. The heat created is used to heat the water in the master heat exchanger.

Title: Satronic control box module 240v
